{"tid":1634772,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T12:31:45.000Z","uid":312125,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b223231b9441f95ac07b0f69f385989093f1957","tid":1634772,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7708a199d15d739dafda3f99e251c5ec8267778e","tid":1634772,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"之鋒一出聲，馬上踢爆分化五毛所謂休息唔裝修既風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80b9f709d56d12262d788b956f868a17fcb1b388","tid":1634772,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:58:30.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"5fdc1ddefaeee382934ff5cbb5cbf1269b1869f9","tid":1634772,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"相關post嘅連結：<br />\n<br />\n【國際線行動】應盡快整理612後警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【行動核彈】你嘅幫手可以搞冧騰訊同埋新浪！強國人無得用微信微博，順便搞冧深圳內有英文template<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620007</a><br />\n<br />\n全民核彈！全部軍師立即響應美國，草擬制裁港共企業名單！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599761</a><br />\n<br />\n制裁名單template，美國所有國會議員聯絡方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624348</a><br />\n<br />\n制裁名單草稿（英文版）長文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607415</a>"},{"pid":"8dccb9fa204dcb69b0763a35918dfa468b665818","tid":1634772,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34abd8f21277eccbdd44d6fbbfda64e41f3fe7ff","tid":1634772,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"推行動post"},{"pid":"339d1e36d34fd800466a001f8bad40de4c06e469","tid":1634772,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"你這樣也杜絕不了連登的三毛和熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63f83fe2529738155dc09030c71a6e598c1a26c","tid":1634772,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339d1e36d34fd800466a001f8bad40de4c06e469","tid":1634772,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"你這樣也杜絕不了連登的三毛和熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eadf2e3133c7462685194aa3e6b523c879c2a4","tid":1634772,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65c12abbade7ed44e6ea7be2591fe2c27e46b92b","tid":1634772,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:11:44.000Z","msg":"行動文好緊要"},{"pid":"2ca63a2b09703b745082660b347a